column27: Sales Performance
1. What is the total sales revenue?
2. Which product category generated the highest sales?
3. What is the average order value (AOV)?
4. Which day, month, or quarter had the highest sales?
5. What is the trend of total sales over time? (daily, monthly, etc.)
Customer Analysis
6. How many unique customers made purchases?
7. Who are the top 10 customers by total spend?
8. What is the gender-wise distribution of customers?
9. Is there a pattern in purchasing behavior by age group?
10. Do males or females spend more on average?
Product-Level Insights
11. Which product category sells the most units?
12. Which product category is the most profitable?
13. What is the average price per unit per category?
14. Which product category is popular among different age groups?
Time-Based Patterns
15. Which days of the week see the highest sales?
16. What is the seasonal trend in sales (Q1, Q2, etc.)?
17. Are sales increasing or decreasing over time?
